      Guidance
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Waiting to return to the UK during coronavirus (COVID-19)
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Guidance for British people who are currently travelling abroad and are unable to return home due to the coronavirus (COVID-19) pandemic.  </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
